{"tid":2183644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳今日起實施生活垃圾分類管理條例 違者罰款50元","createTime":"2020-09-01T05:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T08:09:57.000Z","uid":166360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d8b50e3060afc03cf94c6eb7a5d7f173e50edb","tid":2183644,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"深圳今日起實施生活垃圾分類管理條例 違者罰款50元<br />\n2020-09-01 HKT 08:17<br />\n<br />\n&quot;深圳由今日起，實施生活垃圾分類管理條例，未按規定分類投放生活垃圾的人士，將被罰款50元人民幣，情節嚴重的罰款200元。<br />\n<br />\n深圳將開展垃圾分類執法檢查，9月份是警示期，10月起，對不開展垃圾分類等行為正式開罰。如果受罰的市民沒有嚴重情節，可以通過參加生活垃圾分類培訓、宣傳服務或者現場督導等活動代替罰款......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547119-20200901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547119-20200901.htm&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7qQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=765e9dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547119-20200901.htm&h=86c99da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547119-20200901.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a5870304ef6d59e74423e23409ab38e46c5d990b","tid":2183644,"uid":65638,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"日本係自覺<br />\n支那係靠刑罰<br />\n大和民族比胡種優勝"},{"pid":"5be66aa592150944c35a6282cafa59ed5decf3c0","tid":2183644,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"扔垃圾會有咩嚴重情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"f8e0a1715238e640cd47017147978f6bd7843713","tid":2183644,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"咁成個中囯國已經係垃圾一類要焚化<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩類要分？"},{"pid":"a720816a5061219c7cf3559de555e7e94eae97f9","tid":2183644,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5be66aa592150944c35a6282cafa59ed5decf3c0","tid":2183644,"uid":45910,"like":0,"d